				<a href="https://github.com/matt-cochran/mcp-flowgate/blob/main/LICENSE" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-300">Apache-2.0</a>.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="flex gap-12">
			<div>
				<p class="text-slate-400 font-medium text-sm mb-2">Resources</p>
				<ul class="space-y-1">
